Test 1: Create outer and inner
Outer constructor, value=100
Inner constructor, value=200
Inner.displayBoth():
  this.value (inner) = 200
  Outer.this.value (outer) = 100

Test 2: Modify both values
Modifying values:
  this.value (inner) = 300
  Outer.this.value (outer) = 400
Outer value from outside: 400

Test 3: Display again
Inner.displayBoth():
  this.value (inner) = 300
  Outer.this.value (outer) = 400
